1. *Uglu* stoji kutija sa knjigama. (In the corner, there is a box with books.)
2. Videli smo ga kako stoji *u uglu* sobe. (We saw him standing in the corner of the room.)
3. Kada sam se vratila, pas je bio skriven *iza ugla*. (When I came back, the dog was hidden behind the corner.)
4. Oni su pronašli skriveni dragulj *u nekom uglu* dvorca. (They found a hidden jewel in some corner of the castle.)
5. Moramo da se okrenemo *uglu* da bismo stigli do prodavnice. (We need to turn the corner to get to the store.)
6. *Uglovi* pravougaonika su uvek 90 stepeni. (The angles of a rectangle are always 90 degrees.)
7. Ova zgrada ima vrlo oštre *uglove*. (This building has very sharp corners.)
8. Razgovarali smo o problemima *iz različitih uglova*. (We talked about the problems from different angles.)
9. Baka je isplela čarape *u obliku ugla*. (Grandma knitted socks in the shape of a triangle.)
10. *Uglovi* oka su veoma osetljivi. (The corners of the eye are very sensitive.)